學位抑或係去嘗試下唔同嘅行業<br />\n<br />\n因為到你大個有咗唔同嘅負擔 你會發現根本你就唔會有機會去做囉<br />\n當你努力過都仲係要做港奴嘅時候 起碼你有嘗試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做人處事待人接物 三思而後行 所有行前動都要諗一諗個結果 唔好做一啲或者講一啲返唔到轉頭嘅事同埋說話 <br />\n<br />\n同埋好好愛自己嘅父母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"8addc27dc17f6c072bcc54b04983c1babc52a609","tid":994181,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T22:39:05.000Z","msg":"早走早著，香港呢啲垃圾地方冇撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917b49d0ae95a6a5718d55b0c9b23f3c65e32af0","tid":994181,"uid":38462,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:14:05.000Z","msg":"咪撚讀工程"},{"pid":"a32b564f89b4935da22c980890ffae334da31832","tid":994181,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8addc27dc17f6c072bcc54b04983c1babc52a609","tid":994181,"uid":70301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T22:39:05.000Z","msg":"早走早著，香港呢啲垃圾地方冇撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:16:34.000Z","msg":"X2"},{"pid":"6806697a9a1401dc0169bd71351b63e86b7d12a1","tid":994181,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:17:55.000Z","msg":"唔好儲錢<br />\n<br />\n你辛辛苦苦儲十年，<br />\n人地父幹已經秒哂你所有努力，<br />\n真係倒不如搵幾多洗幾多，<br />\n香港既生活已經成個地獄咁，<br />\n無謂再加倍自己既痛苦"},{"pid":"ab14b7f3730b9c14696b398e2b30dd3f97c98555","tid":994181,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6806697a9a1401dc0169bd71351b63e86b7d12a1","tid":994181,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:17:55.000Z","msg":"唔好儲錢<br />\n<br />\n你辛辛苦苦儲十年，<br />\n人地父幹已經秒哂你所有努力，<br />\n真係倒不如搵幾多洗幾多，<br />\n香港既生活已經成個地獄咁，<br />\n無謂再加倍自己既痛苦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T23:43:25.000Z","msg":"唔儲錢點移民啊！"},{"pid":"423a8214e5dd1c05c336e3b2fd5ac549014748f8","tid":994181,"uid":33099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01